description:
Mobsteel follows a Detroit-area-based custom-car shop transform vintage American cars into modern-day street machines. With founder Adam Genei and his team of custom-car specialists, including his wife Pam, they restore vehicles ranging from relics of the American automotive boom to an old International Harvester Loadstar, and much more. Mobsteel is an existing custom-car shop that was founded more than 10 years ago, using vintage parts and Detroit steel to bring ancient American cars back to life.
